[DQR.US.0101.9538] The concept ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForSharebasedPayments appears in the financing cashflows of the companies cash flow statement. ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForSharebasedPayments is an operating item and it is expected that this item would only appear in the cash flow from operating activities. Please review the calculations defined for the cash flow statement to determine that the correct element has been used for this item.
